<p class="text"><strong>CREATING AN ORDER SITE</strong></p>
<p class="text">To create a new order site, click on &quot;new order site&quot; and
    choose a name for the order site. You may base the new site on an existing
    order site,
  or create an order site with the default settings.</p>
<p class="text">Before making your order site live, you will want to customize the site's appearance 
  and add items to the catalog. For more information, see the following:</p>
